TextEng: Okay... okay, everything is okay... it's okay... thanks for... calming me down...
Text: 좋아... 좋아, 다 괜찮아... 괜찮아... 고마워... 진정시켜 줘서...

TextEng: More undead?! More?! Get away or... I'll get the MUFFFINS!!
Text: 언데드가 더?! 더 있어?! 저리 가 아니면... 머핀 던질 거야!!

TextEng: GAH!!! Take the muffins and GO!! Muffins and go!!!
Text: 악!!! 머핀 가져가고 꺼져!! 머핀이랑 꺼지라고!!!

TextEng: Get away, get away!
Text: 저리 가, 저리 가!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> NO! NO! Too MANY! UNDEAD! EVERYWHERE!
Text: <StartCheck>[실패]</Start> 안 돼! 안 돼! 너무 많아! 언데드가! 사방에!

TextEng: Don't know... don't know! Just gonna RUN!!!
Text: 몰라... 몰라! 그냥 뛸 거야!!!

TextEng: FOLLOW! Gotta follow... past the zombies... PAST THE ZOMBIES!!!
Text: 따라가! 따라가야 해... 좀비들 지나서... 좀비들 지나서!!!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Success]</Start> Wha... what? Who are you... Undead... there's undead everywhere.
Text: <StartCheck>[성공]</Start> 뭐... 뭐야? 누구야... 언데드... 사방에 언데드가 있어.

TextEng: Just stay here... okay... with the zombies... keep low... yeah....
Text: 그냥 여기 있을래... 좋아... 좀비들이랑... 몸 낮추고... 응....

TextEng: Shining Serpent... right... okay... I'll run... I RUN!!
Text: 빛나는 구렁이... 맞아... 좋아... 뛸게... 뛴다!!

TextEng: Uh... uh... there's a tavern... Shining Serpent I think... and, uh... the Helmite sanctuary. That too... maybe. Somewhere.
Text: 어... 어... 선술집이 있어... 빛나는 구렁이인가... 그리고, 어... 헬름 성역. 그것도... 아마. 어딘가에.

TextEng: Follow... okay... okay, I'll follow you... You're safe... okay... following, yes indeed...
Text: 따라가... 좋아... 좋아, 따라갈게... 안전해... 좋아... 따라간다, 그래...

TextEng: They're....EVERYWHERE!! EEEEARGH!!
Text: 걔네가.... 사방에!! 으아아악!!

TextEng: Get away! EAAAAGHHH!!!
Text: 저리 가! 으아아아!!!

TextEng: The Helmites... okay... Temple of Helm... here I go... here I GO!
Text: 헬름 신자들... 좋아... 헬름 신전... 간다... 간다고!

TextEng: You are <race>... Okay.... Okay... maybe you are okay. There's just... undead... everywhere!
Text: <race>구나... 좋아.... 좋아... 아마 괜찮겠지. 그냥... 언데드가... 사방에!

TextEng: It's a trick... a trick... I can tell they are mean... I know!! UNDEAD!!! EVERYWHERE!!!
Text: 속임수야... 속임수... 걔네 나쁜 거 알아... 알아!! 언데드!!! 사방에!!!

TextEng: Know anything... I don't know... I just see them everywhere. I'm sorry... I don't know anything.
Text: 뭘 아냐고... 몰라... 그냥 사방에 보여. 미안해... 아무것도 몰라.

TextEng: I don't think I could have made it... without help... Zombies everywhere... Was it you? I'm just glad to be alive...
Text: 도움 없이는... 살아남지 못했을 거야... 사방에 좀비가... 당신이야? 그냥 살아서 다행이야...

TextEng: Just... leave me be. Zombies... everywhere. I almost died...
Text: 그냥... 가만 내버려 둬. 좀비가... 사방에. 죽을 뻔했어...
